sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Router<br/>(Platform Ingress)
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy /<br/>Gateway API / OAuth)
    participant HTTP as vllm-spyre HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as vllm-spyre gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre<br/>Hardware Accelerator
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC / HF Hub)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup

    Engine->>Storage: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / AWS IAM
    Storage-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>Spyre: Load model onto accelerator<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Model ready

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS (external)
    KServe->>AuthProxy: Forward request
    AuthProxy->>HTTP: HTTP/8000<br/>Plaintext (in-cluster)<br/>Auth: delegated to platform
    HTTP->>Engine: Process inference
    Engine->>Spyre: Offload computation<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>HTTP: Completion response
    HTTP-->>AuthProxy: JSON response
    AuthProxy-->>KServe: Forward response
    KServe-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS protocol)

    Client->>KServe: gRPC GenerationService.Generate<br/>HTTPS (external)
    KServe->>AuthProxy: Forward request
    AuthProxy->>GRPC: gRPC/8033<br/>Plaintext (in-cluster)<br/>Auth: delegated to platform
    GRPC->>Engine: Process inference
    Engine->>Spyre: Offload computation<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>GRPC: gRPC response
    GRPC-->>AuthProxy: Forward response
    AuthProxy-->>KServe: Forward response
    KServe-->>Client: gRPC response
